data.description: Welcome to this charming, spacious, well-maintained home.    Once inside, you'll be impressed by the beautiful hardwood floors that flow throughout the main level, exuding warmth and elegance. The main floor has a living room and dining room that is an open and flexible layout, allowing various furniture arrangements and versatile living spaces.    As we know, convenience is key, and this home has it covered. The main level also hosts a full bathroom, a bonus room to use as a bedroom or office, and a laundry room, adding ease and efficiency to your daily routine.  The kitchen is also large and is great as it is or holds tremendous potential if you desire something more.    As you travel upstairs, you'll be captivated by the gorgeous stairway in the foyer. This architectural feature adds character and even more charm.    Upstairs, you'll discover three well-appointed bedrooms and newer carpet.  You will also find a second full bathroom and plenty of attic space.    This home offer tons of space and two entries and a BRAND NEW FURNACE!  The backyard offers plenty of green space and ample off-street parking for three cars.  Home is back on the market at no fault of the home but due to the previous buyer.
